原福岛核电站的技术人员小仓志郎在接受采访时表示，希望能尽快终止排海。

 #Nuclearwastewater #NUCLEAR https://t.co/iEt0iRepZu

This is the price that Japan, which boasts itself a sense of refined egoism, is bound to pay. The Japanese government is turning a blind eye to the crying of its own fishermen and those working in the aquaculture industry.
